{"word":"ἄμορφος","slug":"ἄμορφος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄμορφος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μορφή'><el>μορφή</el></a>\n<p/><i>misshapen, unsightly</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>: —<a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a> <el>ἀμορφέστατος</el> (as if from <el>ἀμορφής</el>), <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; but <a href='S:regular, regularly'>regul.</a> form <el>-ότερος, -ότατος</el>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/>"}]}